  "texts": [
    "We compare this value with E 0 to confirm that we have reached chemical accuracy.",
    "In the two steps highlighted above, we use error mitigation to compute the minimal energies of Ĥ qubit (r) (see Supplementary Section 8).",
    "For any initial random parameters and bond lengths, the algorithm consistently converges to the theoretical eigenvalues in 50 to 100 iterations (see Fig. 2a).",
    "The entire experiment time per bond length is approximately four times faster than past photonic VQE experiments of a system with the same number of degrees of freedom 40.",
    "At fixed initial conditions and r opt, chemical accuracy was achieved with a success probability of 93%, with greater accuracy than recent photonic VQE experiments 43."
